data.description: Affordable bungalow in district 6! Recent updates to include New roof in 2020, new window world windows with warranty in 2023, New Vinyl siding 2023, New Water Heater 2022.  Outdoor unit replaced 2021.  Termite treatment with bond and vapor barrier 2023.  This adorable home is just waiting for you.  Affordability with convenience to area shopping, restaurants and highways. Large open floorplan, with great room, eat in kitchen, center island stove with downdraft. 2 Large bedrooms and laundry/mud room.  The master and hall have access to the recently renovated bath with tiled shower.  This corner property has a large completely fenced in yard with access from both streets. Home is sold as is. Seller may lease purchase or creative finance with a large downpayment.
